 have a level 19 rogue on tunare.I love him but i was thinking of starting a PvP character. I have herd that there is no feeling like takeing down someone else higher level than you.So i have a few questions:<br>
1.What are the looting rules on the servers? I am thinking of starting on the race war server.<br>
2.What is a good class for PvP?Well maybe the question should be if rogues are good at PvP?<br>
3.What are the groups on the race war server? Is it like good vs. bad?OR are there more groups?<br>
4.Okay last question can rogues pp other PC's on PvP servers?<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukhaunshar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Khaunshar</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/14/01 10:19:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=148.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A few questions about PvP servers</span><hr size=1> 1. Would like to know that myself. I know Rallos Zek is coin + 1 item, dont know about Tallon and Vallon<br>
<br>
2. Another thing where I d love some info as well.. although my question is : Does a monk make a decent pvp char into the 30s ? Not saying I want to own everything alive, but not getting owned all the time certainly helps a lot.<br>
<br>
3. Groups are:<br>
 I: Dark Races: Ogres, Trolls, Iksar, Dark Elves<br>
 II: Elven Races: High Elves, Wood Elves, Half Elves<br>
 III: Humans: Humans, Barbarians, Erudites<br>
 IV: Short Races: Dwarves, Halflings, Gnomes<br>
Actually, there seems to be a kind of unwritten agreement with a Dark vs Light kind of playing... essentially meaning all vs Team I. Makes more sense roleplaying wise to me as well<br>
<br>
4. No<br>
<br>
5. I d like to add my own question here, rather than opening a new thread: I hear everyone talk about bags, I assume you cant take a won item out of a bag, meaning bag items are safe? Confirmation would rock.<br>
<br>
 <p>@~}~~   Khaunshar T'Varith   ~~{~@</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulirintz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lirin TZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/14/01 10:28:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=148.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A few questions about PvP servers</span><hr size=1> well, welcome to the wonderfull world of PKing.  <br>
<br>
1.  rallos is item loot, one item off your dead enemys corpse.  tallon and vallon are both coin only loot, all the money on your dead enimys body.  <br>
<br>
2.  rouges are pretty strong at pvp.  first they are melee, so you will NEVER get jumped while you are medding or lom, second we have those nifty backstabs.  now casters do own untill you get some decent MR gear, so take that into consideration, but once a melee gets that they are hard to stop.  <br>
<br>
3.  teams are shorts v blinds v elfs v darks.  if you are one you can get PKd by anyone in your range (+/- 8) on any other team.  most of the server plays good v evil though, so unless you run into specific guilds that are one team pk guilds(lotu, hr, fs), you should be all right unless you run into darkys.  <br>
<br>
4.  dont think so.  never tryed it though...<br>
<br>
