</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulirintz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lirin TZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/14/01 10:29:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=148.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A few questions about PvP servers</span><hr size=1> right, cant loot from bags on rallos. <p><img src="http://www.geocities.com/drunkmonkus/CoNForever.jpg"> 
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufricka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fricka</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/shanks/teenyknot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/14/01 10:46:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=148.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/Sigs/4FrickaNEWlt.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A few questions about PvP servers</span><hr size=1> 1. Vallon is coin only loot<br>
<br>
2. Rogues are more challenging at PvP and take awhile to come into our own with the best levels coming at mid levels.<br>
<br>
3. There are 4 Teams on the race war servers.<br>
1 Blue/Human Team (Barbs, Erudites, Humans<br>
2 Yellow/Elven Team (High elves, half elves, and wood elves)<br>
3 Purple/Short Team (Gnomes, dwarves, halflings)<br>
4 Orange/Dark Team (ogres, trolls, dark elves and iksar-very few iksars on our server)<br>
<br>
Tallon Zek has more &quot;good versus evil&quot; teams on the server while Vallon Zek has more pure team guilds: The Shanks (a Safehouse guild) being one of them.<br>
<br>
4. No you can't.  There was an unconfirmed report of rogues who turned in their books being able to pickpocket from others who turned in their books (you DO NOT need to do this on a PvP server) but I have never heard of an incident occuring.<br>
<br>
