<br>
Now, best PvP class is how well you play. I feel mages are best due to the pets. Necros are second. Now druids would be cool, but I hate playing casters. I know that I have killed my fair share and they have killed me as well. <br>
<br>
But a KEY rule.  <br>
<br>
Its a game, dont get pissed, even though you will be mad. <br>
<br>
My stress level rises when I play on Rallos..maybe the Tallon/Vallon are better...good luck either way.<br>
<br>
